{
  "texts": [
    "Our current implementation only supports users to inject documents as context in the prompt, but no hints are provided to show which documents are indeed used by the agent.",
    "It would be more useful if the system could show the referenced documents in the agent's response and link them back to the visualizations.",
    "In addition, comparative sensemaking of different clusters is also a wanted feature from the participants.",
    "Although users of HINTs could inject documents from two different clusters and ask the agent for comparisons, it is not intuitive and the comparison made by the agent is not satisfactory.",
    "Participants would like to have more control over what to compare and a graphical representation of the comparison result."
  ]
}